attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles the rolling cart. He first flips the furniture and removes the wheels. Then he unscrews the trays and withdraws them one by one. Next, he unscrews the sidebars, at last, splits the base frame.

attributes.Transcription: We will now disassemble a trolley from IKEA.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the top tray.
The student disassembles the middle tray.
The student disassembles the bottom tray.
